headline: Toast Accelerates Restaurant Growth While Block Leans on Cash App to Offset Square Slowdown
summary: Toast (NYSE: TOST) and Block (NYSE: SQ) both reported Q3 2025 earnings that beat revenue estimates but missed on EPS. Toast powers 156,000 restaurant locations with payment and operations software. Block runs Square for sellers and Cash App for consumers.
